      "text": "6. Un jepſchu tas diwi tuhſtoſchus Gaddus dſihwohtn/ tad tomehr wiſch labbu ne reds.\nNeggi wiſſi eet uhs weenu Weetu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Wiſs Darbs ta Zilweka ma eet/ neka Dſihru-Naimna irr preekſch ſawas Mutteſ/ bet jo eeſch winna irr tas Gale wiſta Strds ne irr pildama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Jo kaſ attezz tam Gudram wairak neka Geckam? Kaſ irr tam Nabbagam wairak/ kaſ neeekſch teem Dſihweem finna staigaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Labbakis irr tas/ kaſ ar Azim tohp redſehts/ neka pehz to ta Sirde dsennahs/ ir tas irr Nelectiba un Sirde-Wahrgoſchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Laid irr kahe buhdams/ wiſna Wahrs jaw irr nofaukte/ un irr ſinnams/ ka tas weens Zilweks irr/ un ne mahk teefaht ar ta/ kaſ ſtipraks irr/ neka wiſsch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Teefcham/ dauds Leetas irraid/ kaſ to Neleetibu wairo/ kaſ tad tam Zilwekam wairak\n(no ta) attezz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta VII. Nodalla.\nSalamans mahza/ ka labba Slawa weena labba Leeta ekus: 2. Un ſtahſta zittus Darbus/ furreem teem Deewabihjigeem buhs pakkat,\ndſhteeg: 3/ 6/ 10. xc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "1. O kaſ finna/ kaſ tam Zilwekam par Labbu irr ſchinui Dſihwoſchana/ tamehr wiſch ſawa Neleetiba dſihwo/ ko wiſch pawadda ka Ebua: Jo kuſch warr Zilwekam ſtahſtibt/ kaſ pehz winnu notiks appakſch Saules.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Labbaka irr weena labba Slawa/ neka falda Etje/ utahs Mirſchanas Deena/ neka ta Deena eeſch ka kaſ peedſem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Labbaki irr Waidu-Nam\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fo Zilweku/ un tas kaſ dſihwo leck to pee ſawas Sirde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Noſkumschana irr labbak neka Smeeschana/ jo zaun ta Waiga Noſkumschanu tohp ta Sirde labbaka darrita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Ta Sirde to Gudru ir Watdu-Naimna/ bet to Geck Sirde irr Libgimoſchana Namna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Labbakis irr ta Gudra Lam matchanu klaufht/ neka kaſ klaufa ta Gecka Dſeeſmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Jo ka to Ehrſchſtu Braſch keſchana appakſch kahta Pob da irr/ taſatt irr ta Gecka Sineſchana/ tas irr arri Nelectiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Teefcham/ ta Apbehding Schana warretu arri weenu Gud ru trakſu padarriht/ un Dah wanaz famaita to Sirde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Labbakis irr kaudas Leeta Galſ/ neka winnas Gefahkums Weens Lehnprahtigajs irr lab baks/ neka weens Leptnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Ne effi ahtrſtawa Brah ta dusmoht/ jo ta Duſnib duſs to Gecku Asoti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Ne takki: Kaſ tas irr/ ka tee preekſchaji Laiki labbaki biju ſchi neka ſchee? Jo tu ar Gudri bu to ne waiza.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Gudribn irr labba ar kal da\n"
    }
  ],
